WEBVTT

00:04:29.183 --> 00:04:32.298
and now when we meet it’s
like meeting old friends.

00:04:33.036 --> 00:04:39.069
We give each other the respect
and freedom to live life on our terms.

00:04:39.069 --> 00:04:40.180
Think about it.

00:04:40.180 --> 00:04:42.267
“If, with the thread 
of the 100 Saree Pact

00:04:42.636 --> 00:04:47.858
we can build ties 
that are so strong,

00:04:47.858 --> 00:04:50.393
why can’t we do the same in society?”

00:04:50.844 --> 00:04:54.627
We just lack the ability 
to recognize that link,

00:04:54.627 --> 00:04:58.551
that thread that bind our thoughts,

00:04:58.551 --> 00:05:00.802
opinions and differences --